== '''Ubuzima bwe bwite''' ==

=== Ubuto bwe n'umuryango ===
Elumelu yavukiye i [[:en:Jos|Jos]], Plateau<ref>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Plateau_State</ref>, muri Nijeriya, ku ya 22 Werurwe 1963, avuka kuri Suzanne na Dominic Elumelu ukomoka muri Onicha-Ukwu muri Aniocha y'Amajyaruguru y’akarere ka Leta ya [[:en:Delta_State|Delta]]<ref>https://theeagleonline.com.ng/gov-okowa-eulogises-tony-elumelu-at-55/</ref><ref>https://guardian.ng/life/tony-elumelu-the-quintessential-leader/</ref> Yakuranye na barumuna be bane, umwe muri bo ni Ndudi Elumelu, umuyobozi muto mu nteko ishinga amategeko ya Nigeriya ('''Nigerian Federal House of Representatives)'''<ref>https://encomium.ng/20-things-about-tony-elumelu-man-of-means-who-donates-billions/</ref><ref>https://www.nassnig.org/mps/single/10</ref>

=== Uburezi (Education) ===
Yize ibijyanye n'ubukungu muri kaminuza ya Leta ya Bendel (ubu ni [[:en:Ambrose_Alli_University|kaminuza ya Ambrose Alli]]) ahabwa impamyabumenyi ya BSc na Master of Science in Economics yakuye muri kaminuza ya Lagos.<ref>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Lagos</ref>

== '''Umwuga''' ==

=== Umwuga we wa mbere ===
Elumelu yakoze muri Banki y’ubumwe ya Banki ya Nijeriya (Nigerian Bank Union Bank) nk'umunyamuryango w’Urubyiruko muri National youth Service Corps mu 1985 mbere yo gutangira umwuga we wo gucuruza. Muri 2005 Elumelu yaguze imigabane muri banki za leta zose, nyuma aguze na Banki yunze ubumwe ya Afrika (UBA).

Mu mwuga we wa mbere, yagize ati;<blockquote>Natangiye umwuga wanjye w'ubucuruzi, ngurisha copi z'impapuro kugira ngo mbe umwihariko,nari muto kandi nshonje, ndetse nkora cyane, ariko ikigaragara ni uko nari umwe gusa mu bihumbi by’abasore barangije muri Nijeriya, bose bifuzaga gutsinda<ref>https://www.thecable.ng/years-of-spreading-luck-everyone-needs-a-little-help/</ref>.</blockquote>Mu 1997, Elumelu yayoboye itsinda rito ry'abashoramari, ahita ashyiraho banki yitwa (struggling crystal bank) nyuma yigihe gito bayihindurira izina bayita (Standard Trust Bank). Yahinduye inyungu mu myaka mike maze muri 2005 ahita azamurwa mu intera nini mu rwego rw’amabanki muri Afurika yo munsi y’ubutayu bwa Sahara agura Banki yunze ubumwe ya Afurika (UBA)<ref>https://www.proshareng.com/news/Capital-Market/Elumelu-is-MD-of-UBA---Merger-of-UBA-STB/111</ref><ref>https://www.forbes.com/sites/mfonobongnsehe/2014/12/01/nigerian-billionaire-tony-elumelu-commits-100-million-to-create-10000-african-entrepreneurs-in-10-years/?sh=3570539b2d47</ref>. Nyuma y’ihuzwa rya Standard Trust Bank na Banki yunze ubumwe ya Afurika muri 2005, Elumelu yayoboye iyi sosiyete nk'umuyobozi ushinzwe amatsinda kuva mu itsinda ry’amabanki yo mu gihugu kimwe kugeza muri banki ya Afurika ifite amashami mu bihugu 20 bya Afurika, Ubufaransa, Amerika n'Ubwongereza kugera igihe yeguriye k'ubutegetsi muri 2010, nyuma yo kuva muri board ya UBA yahise ashora imari ye ashyiraho umuryango mugari uzwi nka [[Heirs Holdings]] abikorana n'ibikorwa by'urukundo binyuze mu muryango '''The Tony Elumelu Foundation'''<ref>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Tony_Elumelu_Foundation</ref> <ref>https://www.forbes.com/sites/mfonobongnsehe/2014/12/01/nigerian-billionaire-tony-elumelu-commits-100-million-to-create-10000-african-entrepreneurs-in-10-years/?sh=3570539b2d47</ref>muri 2010 nyuma yo kujya muzabukuru, kugera uyu munsi uyu muryango uracyakora ibikorwa by'urukundo kuko ufasha urubyiruko guteza imbere imishinga yabo y'ubucuruzi<ref>https://books.google.com/books?id=JgdZDwAAQBAJ&dq=TONY+ELUMELU+AFRICAPITALISM&pg=PR3</ref>.

