== '''Ibihembo n'Ishimwe yahawe''' ==
Elumelu yakiriye ibihembo bitandukanye ashimirwa uruhare rwe mubucuruzi no kwihangira imirimo.

* Mu 2003 leta ya Nijeriya yahaye Elumelu izina ry'umunyamuryango w'iteka rya Repubulika (title of Member of the Order of the Federal Republic(MFR),nk'icyubahiro cy'igihugu<ref>https://www.thecable.ng/tony-elumelu-making-business-ambassador</ref>
* Mu mwaka wa 2012, yahawe igihembo cy’icyubahiro cy’igihugu cy’umuyobozi w’itegeko rya Nigeriya (CON) kubera uruhare yagize mu guteza imbere imishinga yigenga<ref>https://web.archive.org/web/20150518090635/http://www.thisdaylive.com/articles/adenuga-bags-gcon/124579/</ref> 
* Yahawe igihembo cyitwa 'Daily Times, umugabo w’umwaka wa Nigeriya muri 2016<ref>https://dailytimes.ng/elumelu-won-daily-times-nigeria-man-year-2016/</ref>
* Muri 2018 na 2019 yahawe igihembo cya All-Africa Business Leaders 'Awards (AABLA) Philanthropist of the Year Award <ref>https://techeconomy.ng/2018/11/all-africa-business-leaders-awards-announce-2018-west-african-finalists/</ref>
* Muri 2019 Kaminuza ya Bayero Kano (BUK) yahaye Elumelu - Impamyabumenyi y'ikirenga y'icyubahiro mu bucuruzi <ref>https://www.premiumtimesng.com/business/333636-buk-to-honour-tony-elumelu-with-an-honorary-doctorate-degree.html/</ref>
* Yahawe igihembo cyigihugu cyo gutanga umusaruro wicyubahiro muri 2019 <ref>https://www.thisdaylive.com/index.php/2019/11/27/elumelu-to-receive-national-award/</ref>
* Ikinyamakuru IGIHE (Time Magazine) cyasize Elumelu kurutonde rw'abantu 100 Bakomeye Muri 2020<ref>https://time.com/collection/100-most-influential-people-2020/5888413/tony-elumelu/</ref>.

